{"word":"ἄπιστος","slug":"ἄπιστος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἄπιστος, ον</el></b> [<el>ἀ-</el><a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ priv.\">priv.</a>, <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πιστός\">πιστός</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> of things ‘not worthy of credence’, <b><i>incredible, far-fetched</i> <a href='B:510 26:8'>Ac 26:8</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> ‘refusing to give credence (to)’, <b><i>without faith/trust, unbelieving</i> <a href='B:490 9:41'>Lk 9:41</a>; <a href='B:500 20:27'>J 20:27</a>; <a href='B:530 6:6'>1 Cor 6:6</a>; <a href='B:540 6:14'>2 Cor 6:14</a>; <a href='B:610 5:8'>1 Ti 5:8</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> <i>faithless, without fidelity/commitment, fickle</i> <a href='B:470 17:17'>Mt 17:17</a>; <a href='B:630 1:15'>Tit 1:15</a>; <a href='B:730 21:8'>Rv 21:8</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπιστία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἁπλότης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}